    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car to believe it. It's in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that's basically brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
