    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is an investment-grade 2017 BMW M2 (F87) in showroom condition. This N55-powered coupe features a twin-scroll turbocharger and an Active M Differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and torque vectoring. The 6-speed manual transmission remains crisp, paired with a factory-spec clutch that shows no signs of slip. The vehicle is strictly stock, retaining its original paint depth and factory-forged wheels without a hint of curb rash. Every service interval has been performed ahead of schedule, ensuring the valvetrain and cooling system operate at peak efficiency. This is a collector-quality example with a completely clean undercarriage and a flawless interior, free from bolster wear or UV damage.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
