    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade vehicle that presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and a recent professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats remain supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively performed at authorized dealerships. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, and the engine bay is detailed to a high standard. Included in the sale are all original keys, the factory tool kit, and a meticulously organized binder of every service receipt since new. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example that satisfies even the most discerning inspection.",
      "price": 43800.0,
